<section id="about">
  <div class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="num">01</span> / ABOUT</div>
  <h2 class="sec reveal d1">Who's behind<br>the screen</h2>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-copy reveal d2">
      <p>I am <b>Chaiyapong Jaroonrotjananan</b>, a Computer Engineering graduate from Kasetsart University (Kamphaeng Saen Campus) with a strong passion for <span class="accent">Software Engineering</span> and Full-stack Development. I specialize in building highly structured backend systems while delivering clean, responsive user interfaces.</p>
      <p>During my cooperative education internship as a <b>Full-stack Developer</b> at <b>App InTouch Co., Ltd.</b>, I gained hands-on experience upgrading enterprise budget systems — refactoring legacy reports, building an automated Excel export engine, and cutting initial page load times with tab-based lazy loading. I excel at handling evolving client requirements, optimizing slow queries, and improving performance using modern techniques.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="player-card reveal d3">
      <div class="pc-head"><span>PLAYER_STATS</span><b>LV.99</b></div>
      <div class="stat-line"><span class="k">ALIAS</span><span class="v">Japan</span></div>
      <div class="stat-line"><span class="k">LOCATION</span><span class="v">Thailand</span></div>
      <div class="stat-line"><span class="k">EDUCATION</span><span class="v">B.Eng. Computer Engineering, Kasetsart Univ. (KPS)</span></div>
      <div class="stat-line"><span class="k">CLASS</span><span class="v">Backend / Full-stack</span></div>
      <div class="stat-line"><span class="k">FOCUS</span><span class="v on">Performance Tuning & Backend Systems</span></div>
      <div class="stat-line"><span class="k">STATUS</span><span class="v on">Open to work</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; gap: 46px; align-items: start; }
  .about-copy p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 620px; }
  .about-copy p b { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .about-copy .accent { color: var(--accent); }
  .player-card { border: 1px solid var(--line); background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--panel), var(--bg-2)); padding: 22px; }
  .player-card .pc-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--faint); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding-bottom: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .player-card .pc-head b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
  .stat-line { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; padding: 11px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; }
  .stat-line:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .stat-line .k { color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .stat-line .v { color: var(--text); text-align: right; }
  .stat-line .v.on { color: var(--accent); }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
